WEBVTT

00:00:00.155 --> 00:00:01.894
My name is Tom,

00:00:01.918 --> 00:00:05.070
and I've come here today to come clean

00:00:05.094 --> 00:00:08.527
about what I do for money.

00:00:08.551 --> 00:00:12.027
Basically, I use my mouth in strange ways

00:00:12.051 --> 00:00:14.217
in exchange for cash.

00:00:14.241 --> 00:00:15.312
(Laughter)

00:00:15.336 --> 00:00:18.511
I usually do this kind of thing
in seedy downtown bars

00:00:18.535 --> 00:00:20.134
and on street corners,

00:00:20.158 --> 00:00:23.230
so this mightn't be
the most appropriate setting,

00:00:23.254 --> 00:00:27.063
but I'd like to give you guys
a bit of a demonstration

00:00:27.087 --> 00:00:30.210
about what I do.